title: Syndra Q
body:
Why?  When u cast {{champion:134}}  Q out of range she walks there and then casts it. This is verry irritating, but when u cast a {{champion:54}}  ult out of range he casts it with full range.  This makes playing with quick cast so much worst ({{champion:134}} ). 
I want to have a simular style syndra Q suck as malp ult
